The URI scheme *'android-app://'* followed by the app [package name](https://apptuse.com/how-to-get-installed-app-package-name-in-android) will open an Android app.

For example, on an Android device, we can use the URI *'android-app://com.google.android.calculator'* in [this](android-app://com.google.android.calculator) link to open the calculator app.
